	Conventions in Java:
		keywords	-	lowercase
		constants	-	UPPER_CASE
		package		-	lowercase
		class/interface	-	PascalCase
		methods/fields	-	camelCase
		
		kebab-case	-	background-color
		snake_case	-	user_name
		
